Hezké, hezké!

107
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:55,240
Trošku se posuň.

108
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:56,760
Jo, jo.

109
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:59,030
<i>Oh, wow!</i>

110
00:07:59,030 --> 00:08:02,230
Hej, to je super.

111
00:08:02,230 --> 00:08:04,410
Její nohy vypadají dobře. 

112
00:08:04,410 --> 00:08:07,000
